        <h3>Your Next Steps</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Write your worthy ideal on a card today</li>
          <li>Begin your 30-day mental discipline challenge</li>
          <li>Define success in your own terms, free from others' expectations</li>
          <li>Commit to serving others abundantly</li>
          <li>Save 10% of everything you earn</li>
          <li>Replace every negative thought with your positive goal</li>
          <li>Read <a href="/blog/vision-to-reality" rel="noopener">how to turn your vision into reality</a></li>
          <li>Build <a href="/blog/habits-discipline-momentum" rel="noopener">sustainable habits that compound</a></li>
        </ol>
